Package: BridgeChange
Type: Package
Title: Bayesian Change-point models with Bridge prior for analyzing time-series and panel data.
Version: 1.2.1
Date: 2018-11-20
Authors@R: c(
  person("Jong Hee", "Park", email = "jongheepark@snu.ac.kr", role = c("aut")),
  person("Soichiro", "Yamauchi", email = "syamauchi@princeton.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
  )
Description: BridgeChange is a package for uncovering time-varying interaction effects in regression models. It implements change-point analysis using Bayesian Bridge prior where regression parameters (including all possible pairwise interactions) are allowed to change multiple times.
License: GPL (>= 2)
Depends: 
    copula,
    MCMCpack, 
    mvtnorm,
    plm,
    Rcpp (>= 0.12.11), 
    tidyr,
    RcppArmadillo
Imports:
    coda (>= 0.11-3),
    pgnorm,
    truncnorm 
LinkingTo: Rcpp, RcppArmadillo
RoxygenNote: 6.1.1
Suggests: knitr,
    rmarkdown
VignetteBuilder: knitr
Encoding: UTF-8
